menu "Wake Word Configuration"

    config WAKE_WORD_ENABLED
        bool "Enable WakeNet wake word detection task"
        default y
        help
            Start the WakeNet wake word detection task after audio initialization.
            The detected wake word can be selected in the ESP Speech Recognition
            menu (provided by esp-sr component).

    config WAKE_WORD_TASK_STACK_SIZE
        int "Wake word task stack size"
        default 8192
        help
            Stack size for the wake word detection task.

endmenu
